      "text": "あけまして\nおめでとうございます",
      "startTime": 7.3333331307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "昨年は本当に\nお世話になりました",
      "startTime": 9.5657140931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_02_01-rui002.wav",
      "text": "私達が日々頑張れるのも――",
      "startTime": 12.6333331307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ストーップ！　固い固い\nお正月から固過ぎや！",
      "startTime": 15.0611107707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
